name: Corvallis_Accent_Cabinet
description: The Corvallis accent cabinet is both stylish and functional. Adorned with a recessed damask pattern on its three door fronts for a stylish ornate look while an interior shelf and a rear cut out for cord management adds function.  A lower shelf between barley twisted legs and bun feet offer a great space for display or storage. Coordinating pull hardware complements the warm wood finish and recessed damask design of the Corvallis. Recessed damask design Three (3) doors Rear cut out for cord management Set includes: One (1) accent cabinet  Materials: MDF, wood, resin Finish: Warm wood finish Weight: 105.6 pounds Dimensions: 35.25 inches high x 47.88 inches wide x 14 inches deepShape: RectangleType: Accent Tables, Cabinets, Console TablesStyle: Traditional, Transitional, ContemporaryMaterial: MDF, Metal, WoodAssembly: Assembly RequiredExact Color: BrownFinish: Wood Finish, Natural FinishColor: BrownStyleContemporary, Traditional, TransitionalMaterialMDF, Metal, WoodTypeAccent Tables, Cabinets, Console TablesFinishNatural Finish, Wood FinishShapeRectangleAssemblyAssembly RequiredColorBrown
